ingredients:
8 green zucchini, cut into round slices
8 yellow squash, cut into round slices
2 cans of stewed tomatoes, drained
Grated jack & cheddar cheese
Oregano
Basil
name: Zucchini Casserole
directions: Parboil zucchini and squash.  Put on bottom of 9x13 pan sprinkle with oregano and basil.  Add stewed tomatoes on top of squash/zucchini.  Cover with grated cheeses.  Bake at 350 ° until bubbly.
description:
Amy Linford Hulme
Susan Hulme’s recipe served at many Hulme dinners.
